        <docTitle refersTo="#resolutionNumber">		Resolution 1471 (2003)</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="4730th">4730th meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2003-03-28" refersTo="#adoptionDate">28 March 2003</docDate></docTitle>
